<!--已授权用户弹窗-->
<template>
    <basic-container>
        <el-dialog 
        title="已授权用户" 
        :visible.sync="showAuthorized"
         @close="closeDialog">
            <avue-crud
             ref="crud"
             v-model="form"
             :option="option"
             :data="data">
            </avue-crud>
        </el-dialog>
    </basic-container>
</template>
<script>
export default {
    name:"authorized-dialog",
    props:{
        showAuthorized:{
            type:Boolean,
            default:false
        }
    },
    data(){
        return{
            form:{},
            data:[],
            option:{
                calcHeight: 210,
                searchMenuSpan:6,
                tip: false,
                border: true,
                index: false,
                viewBtn:false,
                addBtn:false,
                editBtn:false,
                delBtn:false,
                menu:false,
                header:false,
                selection: false,
                column:[
                     {
                        label:"用户账号",
                        prop:"productNo"
                    },
                     {
                        label:"邮箱",
                        prop:"productName"
                    },
                     {
                        label:"手机号",
                        prop:"startTime",
                        type:"datetime",
                    },
                    {
                        label:"姓名",
                        prop:"endTime",
                        type:"datetime",
                    },
                    {
                        label:"部门",
                        prop:"authorized",
                        slot:true
                    },
                    {
                        label:"用户状态",
                        prop:"remaining"
                    },
                    {
                        label:"授权时间",
                        prop:"remaining"
                    },
                    {
                        label:"授权人",
                        prop:"remaining"
                    }
                ]
            }
        }
    },
    methods:{
        closeDialog(){
            this.$emit("close");
        }
    }
}
</script>
